{"tid":259355,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"所有生物都為了生存而逃跑，但人類逃跑就會被罵","createTime":"2017-05-26T22:50:19.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-28T00:29:20.000Z","uid":6892,"like":31,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"568c3d3e3bdfc1e2e52c63fc09e910089e6bb590","tid":259355,"uid":6892,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-26T22:50:19.000Z","msg":"日前產經新聞出了一篇報導，一位年僅 13 歲的日本小女孩寫出了一首詩，連大人看了都不禁幡然淚下！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://buzzorange.com/vidaorange/wp-content/uploads/sites/3/2016/11/14910529_1184023591684459_2133020701396814542_n-e1478064275624.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Fvidaorange%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2Fsites%2F3%2F2016%2F11%2F14910529_1184023591684459_2133020701396814542_n-e1478064275624.jpg&h=3410b676&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n會因為逃跑被罵的<br />\n<br />\n大概只有人類了<br />\n<br />\n其他的生物都順應本能<br />\n<br />\n不逃跑就不能生存<br />\n<br />\n為什麼人類會<br />\n<br />\n「不可以逃」<br />\n<br />\n在遇到困難時，我們總是被勸說「不能逃避現實」，要勇敢面對。但逃避是動物生存本能，為什麼不可以逃？<br />\n<br />\n有時候在身心俱疲的狀況下，還硬要面對困難，只會讓情況越來越糟，撞得頭破血流。這時候如果「逃避」一下，讓自己跳脫泥沼，重新檢視自己的生活、重新思考人生的方向，也許才是對的應對之策。這也是為什麼 Gap year、壯遊、旅行等變成很多人在生活停滯時，做出的選擇。<br />\n<br />\n匈牙利有一句名言：&ldquo;Sz&eacute;gyen a fut&aacute;s, de hasznos.&rdquo;就是這個道理，翻譯成中文是「逃跑雖可恥但卻很有用」，這句話也被翻成日文，變成一部漫畫和日劇（新垣結衣主演，正在播映）。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://buzzorange.com/vidaorange/2016/11/02/poem-about-flee/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbuzzorange.com%2Fvidaorange%2F2016%2F11%2F02%2Fpoem-about-flee%2F&d=HS81ka5Fksfz0dKOxPnR2uI2ZYfPb188nwqbwuz8hpE%3D&h=e0436694\" target=\"_blank\">https://buzzorange.com/vidaorange/2016/11/02/poem-about-flee/</a>"},{"pid":"20fbf63142c3028ea00f88d1a8da22e1a8ed0d5f","tid":259355,"uid":10890,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T00:50:20.000Z","msg":"港豬不知幾叻逃避現實<br />\n邊個話冇得逃避<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4468ca23a836d2d6c5619fdfb8a9bb9eab5d4110","tid":259355,"uid":4402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:07:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>港豬不知幾叻逃避現實<br />\n邊個話冇得逃避<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n逃避同永遠活係自己世界係兩回事黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a476f3483fef24d2034903ac9b06a0bb9d09733","tid":259355,"uid":104077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:08:51.000Z","msg":"捨生取義<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e5f54b5df3b077a8ed0664a29cb4bdc737be5ed","tid":259355,"uid":33848,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:10:10.000Z","msg":"順應本能見女就姦好未<br />\n人有別於禽獸係可以壓抑本能"},{"pid":"18a75c75aab3618a1b6a2b6f2de578173885d525","tid":259355,"uid":27432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:18:05.000Z","msg":"又岩wo, 遇到困難咪揾第二條路行"},{"pid":"136f655959ede987f6b5c6e1abc4b69c70b4924e","tid":259355,"uid":33640,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:23:09.000Z","msg":"動物一樣會為生存而戰鬥啦"},{"pid":"f6be0dac1a0729e88d8979620c3792d3b2f15fea","tid":259355,"uid":51701,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:33:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>順應本能見女就姦好未<br />\n人有別於禽獸係可以壓抑本能</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n為了生存而逃跑 (本能)= 強姦 (本能)"},{"pid":"b74865f3c2787de3edd4ff9b6f06206c9f898324","tid":259355,"uid":54176,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:42:17.000Z","msg":"姦哂d女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49cc82f29edf21ee0a3d46049d29ba2ddfd0ffa5","tid":259355,"uid":66234,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T01:48:52.0